            "title": "",
            "heading_top_margin": 5,
            "heading_margin": 5,
            "text": "<p>By using regenerative jute, we harness a fiber that absorbs 15 tons of CO2 to remain 100% carbon-negative. It’s why we call it the 'Golden Fiber', a material that gives back more than it takes</p>",
